## Nomenclatura BEM

```
sb-ui-{component}                    → Block
sb-ui-{component}--{modifier}        → Modifier
sb-ui-{component}__{element}         → Element
```

**Variables CSS:**
```
--sb-ui-{component}-{property}-{state}
```

